        },
        {
            "id": 23,
            "cardSet": 7,
            "title": "Financial Policies",
            "body": [
                "<p>The City of Asheville financial policies establish general guidelines for the fiscal management of the City.\nThese guidelines, influenced by the North Carolina Local Government Budget and Fiscal Control Act and\nsound financial principles, provide the framework for budgetary and fiscal planning. Operating independently\nof changing circumstances and conditions, these policies assist the decision-making processes of the City Council\nand City administration.</p>"
            ],
