                "<p>State law requires that all municipal governments publish a complete set of financial statements\npresented in conformity with generally accepted accounting principles (GAAP).</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.ashevillenc.gov/Portals/0/city-documents/finance/2014CAFR.pdf\">Fiscal Year Ended June 30, 2014</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.ashevillenc.gov/Portals/0/city-documents/finance/CAFR%2012172013.pdf\">Fiscal Year Ended June 30, 2013</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.ashevillenc.gov/Portals/0/images/departments/finance/CAFR%202013%20with%20changes.pdf\">Fiscal Year Ended June 30, 2012</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.ashevillenc.gov/Portals/0/city-documents/finance/cafr/CAFR%202011.pdf\">Fiscal Year Ended June 30, 2011</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.ashevillenc.gov/Portals/0/city-documents/finance/cafr/CAFR2010.pdf\">Fiscal Year Ended June 30, 2010</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.ashevillenc.gov/Portals/0/city-documents/finance/cafr/2009%20COA%20CAFR.pdf\">Fiscal Year Ended June 30, 2009</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.ashevillenc.gov/Portals/0/city-documents/finance/cafr/CAFR%202008.pdf\">Fiscal Year Ended June 30, 2008</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.ashevillenc.gov/Portals/0/city-documents/finance/CAFR%202007.pdf\">Fiscal Year Ended June 30, 2007</a></li>\n</ul>"
